reviews: Came very quickly (same day) and seems to be good quality so far. I havent messed with the bluetooth hookup, as I dont require that feature for what I need it for. Has three different light types to choose from, and you can brighten/ dim as well.

review_title: The Great Quality You Would Expect
reviews: I purchased the black hat and it came very quickly (same day), and the quality is fantastic. Very warm, not scratchy, no issues with the seam. I know some of the other reviews mentioned issues, possibly with where is was manufactured. The black hat was made in Canada and had all of the proper Carhart tags/labels.

I was a bit skeptical about this purchase, bit very glad I made it. It came slightly damaged and I cant figure out some of the settings, as the instructions are very basic, but over all it is very nice. I've had friends inquire about it when they first saw it as well.
